tatra praviṣṭasyābhiṣiktasya pakṣāntaram āha ||

<commentary>maṇḍala ityādi | etat tantroktamaṇḍala iti bhāvaḥ | samāhito 'nuddhatakāyavāṅmanovyāpārāt | śraddhā abhisampratyayaḥ | yatna udyogaḥ ||</commentary>

gurau upadeśadātari | bhaktaḥ | gurvārādhanakrameṇa kāyavākcittoḥ sevanāt | kṛpāluḥ sarvasattvaduḥkhoddharaṇamānasaḥ | mantrayānaṃ mantranayaḥ |
